  ('Nordic Hamstring Curl', 'nordic-hamstring-curl', 'rehab', NULL, 'Kneel with ankles anchored, lower the torso forward as slowly as possible resisting with the hamstrings, catch with the hands. Prevention RR ~0.49 (Van Dyk meta) — but Impellizzeri''s reappraisal calls it ''inconclusive''; program it, don''t oversell it.', 'Kneel with ankles anchored, lower the torso forward as slowly as possible resisting with the hamstrings, catch with the hands. Prevention RR ~0.49 (Van Dyk meta) — but Impellizzeri''s reappraisal calls it ''inconclusive''; program it, don''t oversell it.', ARRAY['Resist the fall — go as slow as you can','Hips extended, don''t pike','Catch soft, push back to the top'], ARRAY['hamstrings','glutes'], ARRAY['biceps femoris','semitendinosus','semimembranosus'], 'Knee Flexion (Eccentric)', '{}', FALSE, 20, 3, 6, NULL, NULL, 'advanced', '{}', TRUE, ARRAY['hamstring'], 'eccentric', 'neutral', 'moderate', 3, 'META', 3),
