  ('Snap-Down to Stick', 'snap-down-to-stick', 'plyometrics', NULL, 'Landing = decelerating multiples of bodyweight in ~50 ms. Own the STICK before you own the bounce. Progress to firm-but-varied surfaces (turf, single-tilt) — NOT soft pads, which blunt force. Absorb through the hip, quiet the foot.', 'Landing = decelerating multiples of bodyweight in ~50 ms. Own the STICK before you own the bounce. Progress to firm-but-varied surfaces (turf, single-tilt) — NOT soft pads, which blunt force. Absorb through the hip, quiet the foot.', ARRAY['Land soft, absorb through the hips','Stick and hold 2s before you trust the bounce','Quiet foot, knee tracks the 2nd toe'], ARRAY['quadriceps','glutes','hamstrings'], ARRAY['quadriceps','gluteus maximus','hamstrings'], 'Force Absorption / Landing', '{}', TRUE, 16, 4, 6, NULL, NULL, 'intermediate', '{}', TRUE, ARRAY['patellar_tendon','quadriceps','achilles'], 'eccentric', 'neutral', 'high', 6, 'CONSENSUS', NULL),
